Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Today we finished all of the activities scheduled for training.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:13.47,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank God it's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.47,0:00:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo, this isn't the time to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.02,0:00:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have classes for the recording next week in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.23,0:00:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But until then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...You're free!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not happy, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that the recording time will be next week, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll train by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.84,0:00:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you would say that, Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki, if you don't rest a bit, you'll collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't be like you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.89,Op Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Watashi dake mitsumete yo (Only me...)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:21.89,OP Hun,,0,0,0,,Just look at me...(Only me ...)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:25.39,Op Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hokano dareka ga iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.92,0:01:25.39,OP Hun,,0,0,0,,Don't want you looking at anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:33.52,Op Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Todokanai kyori wo ichi miri Motto chijimete...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:33.52,OP Hun,,0,0,0,,Shorten the distance between us even if by only a single millimeter.
