Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:51.60,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1200)\pos(944.8,585)}Blue Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:51.69,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fukusumi Station
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:55.11,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Goodbye! Fukusumi Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.11,0:02:58.90,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Goodbye! Fukusumi Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good one, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:13.46,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you! Fukumsumi Station \ Goodbye Ceremony \ There'll Also Be A Special Presentation With A Famous Idol!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a stage, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to introduce myself in an isolated place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.74,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For Kogure-san's Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,For his father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:30.66,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,Lately, Saya is trying hard, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:36.13,Default Alt Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...she needs to do something more relaxing and rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gure... doing unnecessary things!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't relax once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, Saya-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There sems to be an onsen nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.60,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: "Onsen" is a hot water spring
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Onsen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of delicious foods will be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps seafood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:04:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course wild greens are also delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that she came because she wanted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya-chan, did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Saya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.59,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah... you're not Saya-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Saya-chan was prettier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:28.01,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ah... Onsen, onsen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.01,0:04:33.52,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seems that this onsen is beneficial for your skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a mistake, a mistake...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:38.15,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Will I get ten years younger if I get in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:41.75,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wow, I'll be exactly like Saya-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:43.95,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Could I be a Lemon Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.36,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Just kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.24,0:04:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.61,0:04:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an irresistible reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Saya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishioka-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened for you to look at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Keiko-san hasn't told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The person who's organizing this event is the one that helped you when you were still Yayoi, Nishioka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you can't refuse, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown a lot, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a beautiful woman already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thank you for coming here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.75,0:05:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for you, I'll go anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You learned to speak politely!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishioka-san, Start preparing yourself please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is today's schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The talent is on standby, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that also! It's the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So today's the deactivation ceremony of Fukusumi Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But thinking about it, it's a natural fact that this station stopped to exist, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because only old mamas and papas live here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.47,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.34,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here is a visitor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She really won't find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's too weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's definitely okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did that confidence come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are we doing this on our day off?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Yumi, aren't you worried about Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's root for Saya's work!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.37,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never imagined that Miki-senpai would come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take beautiful photos, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Erika!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki is fascinated with trains..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.35,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is that a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki said that she wanted a picture of Fukusumi Station, since it'll be deactivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I never imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I didn't want to come along with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Saya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're waiting for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... in a while she'll introduce herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,In a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wait a bit then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.00,0:07:46.80,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And one more guest that has decided to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.84,0:07:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya-chan has a lot of fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure does!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, oba-chan, Saya's about to introduce herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.89,0:07:58.60,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: "Oba-chan" is a title given to older women.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:07.19,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm going to introduce you to a special guest that came specially to this end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,About time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The old Yayoi, Yuki Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon to you all that are here at Fukusumi Station!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,I'm Yuki Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.25,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I have to go through with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought some crazy guy came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the guest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's a pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:40.31,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How humiliating!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that you like Fukutsumi eggs, the food that stands out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I eat them everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.70,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanna leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay that you like eggs, but it's weird being dressed as a chicken, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the outfit I dress in everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.25,0:09:00.27,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the clothes you wear everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go shopping like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.55,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No person dresses like this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really like it so much, cluck like a chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, with pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.85,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to smack him after this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.60,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:29.69,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll definiely, definitely smack him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to accept... one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.62,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll smack Gure too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya-chan's work is very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo, Saya, Excellent!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.67,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are they doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya, you imitate very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say that, because next...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Three...! Two...! One...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.78,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll smack all of them later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You surprised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You really look like a chicken like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time, imitate laying an egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone got excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, all Lemon Angel members...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.11,0:10:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They came by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya, it was an amazing presentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.16,0:11:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That outfit was great also.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to dress up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Since little Saya-chan would combine with this costume,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Nishioka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She already dressed up in costumes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she dressed up for other events.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Such as...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Whe we went to Hokkaido, she was dressed up as a sea urchin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we went to Koute, she went as a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we went to Kyoto, she went as Kinkakuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.62,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: Kinkakuji is known as a golden pavilion, who's walls are gold and was built in 1397 in Kyoto. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.62,0:11:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinkakuji is also very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't have random imaginations!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.54,0:11:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How I missed those times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:12:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishioka-san, have you known Saya for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, when Saya-chan was... on some music event for her last job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I knew she got into Lemon Angel, I became scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You got scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that Saya always cried...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:24.07,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: "Nakimushi" has 2 meanings: 1 - insect that sings; 2 - person who cries a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya's
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a Naki-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65  ,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop with those old stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I always had to comfort her behind stage before presentations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop imagining weird things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh~?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.42,0:12:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with those faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, keep up that rhythm in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.01,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have the Station Chief job for the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, I didn't know about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.53,0:13:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you guys think about participating too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Us too??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I want to participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna try!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we, Keiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you have the day off, I'll go ahead and tell the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.08,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.13,0:13:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.63,0:13:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already close to the recording date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And we don't have time to waste at a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You truthfully want to do it with us, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What crazy things are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That time you were taking photos of the Station Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was for the resource that is still to come...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, I can give you the "front play" for the train deactivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's in three hours, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's decided, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Don't decide things for me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The train will arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay behind the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Erika-chan looks so natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too. Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, today is a pretty day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomo-chan, what kind of greeting is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Miru-chan, you can't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ask why.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I trully understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my turn now! Hey, Tomo, now let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be recording next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.71,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And no one is nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've at least gave me the right size.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.26,0:14:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The... The old lady from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When does the next train arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.97,0:14:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ma'am, you should ask that to the real station chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour and twenty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.08,0:15:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She only said that she was waiting for Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Saya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're waiting for your granddaughter who's called Saya
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that visits you during this season, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.99,0:15:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She is exactly the same age as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a person that's as happy as a sunflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:15:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she forgot about this old granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's anxious to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.55,0:16:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be happy if it were like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, can I wait for your granddaughter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't you working now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't much to do, being a station chief for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.29,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, she must arrive with the next train.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oba-chan, the train arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.47,0:17:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya-chan. It's almost closing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So today these six girls worked for us as station chiefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it fun working as a station chief at a station like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't all that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Really! Because I met a lot of different people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There are many rare people that exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You did a good job today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... can I stay a little longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can stay a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:17:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't left yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stay a bit more here. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stay too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard a bit of your conversation earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we wait with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.61,0:18:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My camera's memory is also full.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stay a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it suddenly got busy here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.11,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A plane passed through here, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:25.62,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}On line two, the last train will leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.63,0:19:34.59,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thank you very much for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. That's all, Minaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a letter for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:31.48,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dears,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:36.40,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I spent a lovely time talking with you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:41.20,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to apologize for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:48.66,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To tell the truth, Saya got sick while in Tokyo and had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:53.25,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I couldn't believe it, so I started going to that station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:59.51,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I felt that she really would arrive at anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.42,0:21:03.68,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But when I spoke with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:09.97,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt good because it seemed like I was talking with Saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.72,0:21:13.52,Default Ext,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you very much everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oba-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Saya's a real cry-baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.57,0:21:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not!...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.49,0:21:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, break's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki's up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.80,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hajimete negatta hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:07.80,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Since the first day i laid eyes on you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:16.14,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}nazeka kokoro ga nemuren nakunatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.15,0:22:16.14,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,For some reason my heart can't seem to rest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.90,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}denwa wa suru yuuki mo nai kawari
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.44,0:22:24.90,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,I don't have the courage to pick up the phone and call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:34.79,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}toomawari guuzen wo kiri
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:34.79,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Please, if for only a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:39.71,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}onna no ko tachi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.21,0:22:39.71,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,When girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:43.50,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}koi wo suru ta bi ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:43.50,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,are in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.66,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}sabishigari ni naru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:49.66,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,...They become lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.45,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}itsudaatte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.69,0:22:52.45,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,As they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.70,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.03,0:22:54.70,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:23:09.81,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}nee kono kimochi kimi igai wa arienai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.82,0:23:09.81,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,because when in love, this feeling says no one else but you will do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.67,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Girls in love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.67,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Girls in Love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:18.62,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Motto dakishimete yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.77,0:23:18.62,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,Hold me closer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:28.36,Ed Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yume no naka made tsuretette
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:28.36,ED Hun,,0,0,0,,and take me to a world I can only dream about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:33.93,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,500)}Next Time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.16,0:23:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,With the debut near, the Lemon Angels are finally back?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.91,0:23:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've made it, finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.04,0:23:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.37,0:23:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The program that Yui-senpai destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.67,0:23:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.42,0:23:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki-senpai, you know something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,On the next Lemon Angel Project, episode 11, "Immoral Scenario."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.59,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, the time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.10,0:23:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
